<!-- ====== SERVICE INTRO ====== -->
<section id="service-intro">
  <div class="intro-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-line"></span><span class="eyebrow-text">Deck &amp; Fence Services</span></div>
      <h2 class="section-title">EXTEND YOUR<br>LIVING SPACE.</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule"></div>
      <p class="intro-editorial">"A well-built deck or fence doesn't just add square footage to your home &mdash; it changes <em>how you live in it</em>."</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="intro-body">ETRA Pro Services builds custom decks and installs fences across Halifax, Dartmouth, Bedford, and the entire Halifax Regional Municipality. Whether you need a new backyard deck for entertaining, a privacy fence to define your property line, or repairs to an aging structure, we bring the same attention to detail and honest pricing to every outdoor project.</p>
      <p class="intro-body">We work with <strong>pressure-treated lumber</strong>, <strong>composite decking</strong>, and <strong>cedar</strong> &mdash; matching the right material to your goals, your home's style, and your budget. Every project starts with a free on-site quote and ends with a structure built to last through years of East Coast weather.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ====== CUSTOM DECK BUILDS ====== -->
<section id="deck-builds" class="detail-section bg-char">
  <div class="detail-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-line"></span><span class="eyebrow-text">Deck Construction</span></div>
      <h2 class="detail-h">CUSTOM<br>DECK BUILDS</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule"></div>
      <p class="detail-p">From ground-level platforms to multi-level entertainment decks, we design and build outdoor spaces that fit your property and how you actually use it. Our team handles everything from footings and framing to the finished surface, so you get a single point of contact from start to finish.</p>
      <p class="detail-p">Halifax homeowners know that outdoor structures need to stand up to fog, salt air, freeze-thaw cycles, and heavy snow loads. Every deck we build in Dartmouth, Bedford, and across HRM is engineered for the local climate &mdash; not just built to code, but built to perform.</p>

      <div class="material-tags">
        <span class="mat-tag highlight">Pressure-Treated</span>
        <span class="mat-tag highlight">Composite</span>
        <span class="mat-tag highlight">Cedar</span>
        <span class="mat-tag">Ground-Level</span>
        <span class="mat-tag">Multi-Level</span>
        <span class="mat-tag">Wraparound</span>
      </div>

      <a href="#quote-form" class="btn-gold">Get a Deck Quote &nbsp;&rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-item">
          <span class="info-card-icon">&diams;</span>
          <div>
            <div class="info-card-title">Pressure-Treated Lumber</div>
            <div class="info-card-body">The most popular choice for Halifax decks. Affordable, durable, and treated to resist rot, insects, and moisture. Ideal for homeowners who want a solid deck at a practical price point.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card-item">
          <span class="info-card-icon">&diams;</span>
          <div>
            <div class="info-card-title">Composite Decking</div>
            <div class="info-card-body">Low-maintenance boards that won't splinter, warp, or fade. No staining, no sealing &mdash; just enjoy it. Perfect for busy families and properties in Dartmouth and Bedford where you want the look of wood without the upkeep.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card-item">
          <span class="info-card-icon">&diams;</span>
          <div>
            <div class="info-card-title">Cedar Decks</div>
            <div class="info-card-body">Naturally rot-resistant with a beautiful warm tone. Cedar is a premium choice that ages gracefully and offers a distinctive look that sets your home apart.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card-item">
          <span class="info-card-icon">&diams;</span>
          <div>
            <div class="info-card-title">Complete Build Service</div>
            <div class="info-card-body">Footings, framing, decking, stairs, railings, and finishing details. We handle permits, layout, and the full build &mdash; you just tell us what you want.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

