      <div class="gold-rule"></div>
      <p class="detail-p">Whether you need privacy, security, or simply want to define your property line, ETRA Pro Services installs fences built to handle the Halifax climate. We set every post properly, use quality hardware, and build structures that stay straight and solid through years of wind, rain, and snow.</p>
      <p class="detail-p">From privacy fences that turn your Dartmouth backyard into a retreat, to picket fences that add character to a Bedford front yard, we customize every installation to your lot and your needs. We also handle gate installation, post replacement, and full fence removals when the old one has had its day.</p>

