<!-- ====== REPAIRS & RAILINGS ====== -->
<section id="repairs-railings" class="detail-section bg-char">
  <div class="detail-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-line"></span><span class="eyebrow-text">Repairs &amp; Railings</span></div>
      <h2 class="detail-h">DECK REPAIRS<br>&amp; RAILINGS</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule"></div>
      <p class="detail-p">Not every project needs a full rebuild. If your deck has soft spots, loose boards, or damaged railings, we can repair and reinforce the existing structure &mdash; saving you money while extending its life for years to come. Our team assesses the full condition of your deck before recommending a repair or replacement.</p>
      <p class="detail-p">We also install and replace railings on both new and existing decks across Halifax and HRM. Whether you want wood, aluminum, or glass panel railings, we make sure everything is secure, level, and code-compliant.</p>

      <div class="feature-list">
        <div class="feature-item">Board replacement and resurfacing</div>
        <div class="feature-item">Structural joist and beam repair</div>
        <div class="feature-item">Post and footing reinforcement</div>
        <div class="feature-item">Stair rebuilds and tread replacement</div>
        <div class="feature-item">Wood, aluminum, and glass railing installs</div>
        <div class="feature-item">Fence post replacement and panel repairs</div>
        <div class="feature-item">Full teardown and disposal of old structures</div>
      </div>

      <a href="#quote-form" class="btn-gold">Book a Repair &nbsp;&rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="info-card" style="margin-bottom:28px;">
        <div class="info-card-item">
          <span class="info-card-icon">&diams;</span>
          <div>
            <div class="info-card-title">When to Repair vs. Replace</div>
            <div class="info-card-body">If the footings and framing are sound, a deck resurface or targeted repair is usually the smarter move. We give you an honest assessment &mdash; we won't recommend a full rebuild when a repair will do the job.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-item">
          <span class="info-card-icon">&diams;</span>
          <div>
            <div class="info-card-title">Railing Upgrades</div>
            <div class="info-card-body">Swapping old, weathered railings for new aluminum or glass panels is one of the fastest ways to modernize a deck. It changes the entire look &mdash; and often improves the view from inside your home too.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:28px; padding:22px 28px; background:var(--char2); border:1px solid var(--steel); border-left:2px solid var(--copper);">
        <p style="font-size:12.5px; color:var(--ash); line-height:1.75;"><strong style="color:var(--mist);">Serving all of HRM:</strong> We handle deck and fence repairs in Halifax, Dartmouth, Bedford, Sackville, Fall River, Cole Harbour, Eastern Passage, Timberlea, Hammonds Plains, and surrounding communities.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

